headline.main: SUPPOSED WIFE-POISONING IN BERGEN.; Interesting Testimony Before the Coroner's Jury. THE HUSBAND UNDER ARREST.

docs.lead_paragraph: Coroner GAFFNEY, of Jersey City, commenced an investigation upon the body of Mrs. JANE ABSOM, wife of WM. ABSOM, market gardener, residing at Communipaw, who died very unexpectedly on Friday morning last. Owing to some family difficulty and alleged threats against the life of deceased, her brother, JOHN BENNETT, applied to the Coroner for an investigation.

headline.main: WHAT ISRAEL OUGHT TO DO."; EVENING SERVICE.

docs.lead_paragraph: The congregation in the evening, inside the Church, was no larger than that in the morning, simply because no more could be gotten in, but that on the outside was really tremendous. It would be a good plan for out-door stands to be erected, and the people who crowd at the temple gates could then receive spiritual consolation of one sort, if not the kind they desire.
